(1, '<div id="cc-m-6250559185" class="j-module n j-header " style="padding: 5px; word-wrap: break-word; color: #4e5056; font-family: ''Brandon Text'', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">\n<p id="cc-m-header-6250559185" style="color: #323335; font-size: 2.6rem; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;">Casilla de registro de Jimdo</p>\n</div>\n<div id="cc-m-6250382885" class="j-module n j-hgrid " style="color: #4e5056; font-family: ''Brandon Text'', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; padding: 0px !important;">\n<div id="cc-matrix-1441812885">\n<div id="cc-m-6250382985" class="j-module n j-text " style="padding: 5px; word-wrap: break-word;">\n<p style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Con esta opci&oacute;n tus visitas tendr&aacute;n la oportunidad de acceder a Jimdo directamente.</p>\n</div>\n<div id="cc-m-6250382685" class="j-module n j-text " style="padding: 5px; word-wrap: break-word;">\n<ol style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6em; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; overflow: hidden;">\n<li style="padding-right: 1em; position: relative; right: -1em;">Activa el m&oacute;dulo en "<strong>M&aacute;s m&oacute;dulos</strong>"</li>\n<li style="padding-right: 1em; position: relative; right: -1em;">Elige el bot&oacute;n "<strong>Jimdo</strong>" de la tabla de m&oacute;dulos</li>\n<li style="padding-right: 1em; position: relative; right: -1em;">Guarda los cambios.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div id="cc-m-8246477685" class="j-module n j-htmlCode " style="padding: 5px;">\n<div class="jwl-spacer-s" style="height: 10px;">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div id="cc-m-6250382185" class="j-module n j-text " style="padding: 5px; word-wrap: break-word;">\n<p style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Tras esto aparecer&aacute; la casilla de registro en tu p&aacute;gina, que podr&aacute;s colocar donde quieras. A trav&eacute;s de esta casilla, tus visitantes podr&aacute;n crear una p&aacute;gina JimdoFree directamente desde tu p&aacute;gina JimdoFree.</p>\n<p style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;"><img id="cc-m-imagesubtitle-image-8246477185" class="" style="border: 0px; display: inline; left: 0px; max-width: 100%; top: 0px; vertical-align: top;" src="https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=465x10000:format=png/path/s8a4807607e613aa8/image/idd88aea1635b8855/version/1414510026/image.png" sizes="(min-width: 465px) 465px, 100vw" srcset="https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=320x10000:format=png/path/s8a4807607e613aa8/image/idd88aea1635b8855/version/1414510026/image.png 320w, https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=465x10000:format=png/path/s8a4807607e613aa8/image/idd88aea1635b8855/version/1414510026/image.png 465w, https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/s8a4807607e613aa8/image/idd88aea1635b8855/version/1414510026/image.png 594w" alt="" width="195" height="161" data-src-width="594" data-src-height="490" data-src="https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=465x10000:format=png/path/s8a4807607e613aa8/image/idd88aea1635b8855/version/1414510026/image.png" data-image-id="5532715385" /></p>\n<p style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id="cc-matrix-1441812985">\n<div id="cc-m-8246477185" class="j-module n j-imageSubtitle " style="padding: 5px;">\