(7, '<p style="margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">La forma tradicional de representar la tabla de multiplicar para su memorizaci&oacute;n o repaso es como su propio nombre indica en forma de tabla.<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: 0.6ch;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#cite_note-2">2</a></sup>​<sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: 0.6ch;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#cite_note-3">3</a></sup>​<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: 0.6ch;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#cite_note-4">4</a></sup>​ Donde se multiplica, del uno al diez o del cero al diez, cada uno de los n&uacute;meros.</p>\n<div class="center" style="width: 1124px; text-align: center; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">\n<div class="floatnone" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><a class="image" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg"><img style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg/700px-Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg/1050px-Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg/1400px-Tabla_de_muitiplicar_01.svg.png 2x" alt="Tabla de muitiplicar 01.svg" width="700" height="525" data-file-width="800" data-file-height="600" /></a></div>\n</div>', 10),
(8, '<p style="margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">Las&nbsp;<strong>tablas de multiplicar</strong>&nbsp;se usan para definir la&nbsp;<a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" title="Operaci&oacute;n binaria" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Operaci%C3%B3n_binaria">operaci&oacute;n binaria</a>&nbsp;del&nbsp;<a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" title="Multiplicaci&oacute;n" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiplicaci%C3%B3n">producto</a>&nbsp;para un sistema algebraico. Seg&uacute;n la&nbsp;<a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" title="Correspondencia matem&aacute;tica" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Correspondencia_matem%C3%A1tica">correspondencia matem&aacute;tica</a>:</p>\n<dl style="margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">\n<dd style="margin-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.1em; margin-right: 0px;"><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; opacity: 0;">{\\displaystyle {\\begin{array}{rcl}\\ast :\\;N\\times N&amp;\\to &amp;N\\\\(a,b)&amp;\\to &amp;c=a\\ast b\\end{array}}}</span><img class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: -2.505ex; display: inline-block; width: 26.96ex; height: 6.176ex;" src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/41b0707830882d4b6541fb542b88e80ead86e0eb" alt="{\\displaystyle {\\begin{array}{rcl}\\ast :\\;N\\times N&amp;\\to &amp;N\\\\(a,b)&amp;\\to &amp;c=a\\ast b\\end{array}}}" aria-hidden="true" /></span></dd>\n</dl>\n<p style="margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">de modo que a cada par ordenado (a, b) de&nbsp;<a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" title="N&uacute;mero natural" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C3%BAmero_natural">n&uacute;meros naturales</a>&nbsp;se le asocia un tercer natural c, que es el producto de los dos primeros.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">Las tablas de multiplicar se aprenden en los colegios mediante la&nbsp;<a class="mw-redirect" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" title="Memoria humana" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memoria_humana">memorizaci&oacute;n</a><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: 0.6ch;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#cite_note-1">1</a></sup>​ de los productos de un n&uacute;mero entre 1 y 10 por los sucesivos n&uacute;meros entre 1 y 10.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">Conocida esta tabla y por el&nbsp;<a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" title="Algoritmo de multiplicaci&oacute;n" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algoritmo_de_multiplicaci%C3%B3n">Algoritmo de multiplicaci&oacute;n</a>, se pueden realizar multiplicaciones de cualquier n&uacute;mero de cifras, incluso aunque estas cifras tengan parte decimal.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>\n<div id="toc" class="toc" style="border: 1px solid #a2a9b1; background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 7px; font-size: 13.3px; display: table; zoom: 1; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;">\n<div class="toctitle" dir="ltr" lang="es" style="direction: ltr; text-align: center;">\n<h2 style="color: #000000; background: none; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13.3px; display: inline; line-height: 1.3;">&Iacute;ndice</h2>\n&nbsp;<span class="toctoggle" style="user-select: none; font-size: 12.502px;">&nbsp;[<a class="togglelink" style="color: #0645ad; background: none; cursor: pointer;" tabindex="0" role="button">ocultar</a>]&nbsp;</span></div>\n<ul style="list-style-type: none; margin: 0.3em 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-image: none;">\n<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1" style="margin-bottom: 0.1em;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#Tablas_de_multiplicar"><span class="tocnumber" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: #222222;">1</span><span class="toctext" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;">Tablas de multiplicar</span></a></li>\n<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2" style="margin-bottom: 0.1em;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#La_tabla_de_multiplicar_por_coordenadas_de_la_tabla_pitag%C3%B3rica"><span class="tocnumber" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: #222222;">2</span><span class="toctext" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;">La tabla de multiplicar por coordenadas de la tabla pitag&oacute;rica</span></a></li>\n<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3" style="margin-bottom: 0.1em;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#Otras_tablas_de_multiplicar"><span class="tocnumber" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: #222222;">3</span><span class="toctext" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;">Otras tablas de multiplicar</span></a></li>\n<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4" style="margin-bottom: 0.1em;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#V%C3%A9ase_tambi%C3%A9n"><span class="tocnumber" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: #222222;">4</span><span class="toctext" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;">V&eacute;ase tambi&eacute;n</span></a></li>\n<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5" style="margin-bottom: 0.1em;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#Referencias"><span class="tocnumber" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: #222222;">5</span><span class="toctext" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;">Referencias</span></a></li>\n<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-6" style="margin-bottom: 0.1em;"><a style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;" href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tabla_de_multiplicar#Enlaces_externos"><span class="tocnumber" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: #222222;">6</span><span class="toctext" style="display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;">Enlaces externos</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 13),
